::Key::
Gets the transmission  "Liono in trouble their getting ready to battle in 
space." They may need back up.

::Rinoa::
Rinoa jumps to her feet "Nobody mess my future husband. As soon as I figure 
out how to change Dark Convoy."

::Lilly::
"Shes young still and it scares me. Lets go to plan B." Hang on Koj ((Sound 
advice being cliped to a space ship.)) Goes to the docking bay looks at the 
stasis pods "We are going up in these!"

::WildWing::
"Girls night out huh. Bring me back a something."

::Void::
Void having drones build her something.

::Tiamat::
"If I save that Silver Dragon he'd owe me and I could use some of his 
hoard." As it turns into a tattoo and claws on Lilly.

::BlueStinger::
"We can get there faster with these Transwarp power cells." As she slides 
one into each one of the pods

::Rinoa,Lilly&Tiamat,Key,Bluestinger::
As each climbs into her respective stasis pod the get launched heading 
towards outerspace.
